| 							                                	|
|			 Manual control 			                        |
| 								                                |
| 1) Forward 					                        		|
| 2) Turn right 				                        		|
| 3) Turn left 						                        	|
| 4) Backward 						                        	|
| 5) Stop 							                            |
| 6) Find object 					                        	|
| 7) Find color 					                        	|
| 8) Find colored object 					                    |
| 9) Command sequence 						                    |
| 								                                |
| 0) Back 							                            |
| Q) Exit 							                            |
| 							                                	|
